{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_01_03",
  "title": "神崎莉央",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lizfana",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-lizfana001.m4a",
      "text": "まさかLizNoirが星見市に来るなんてな！\n地方にも優しい莉央たんマジ女神！",
      "startTime": 4.1666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lizfanb",
      "speakerName": "ファンB",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-lizfanb001.m4a",
      "text": "ホント楽しみですよ！\n僕は葵ちゃん命ですけど！",
      "startTime": 9.168831621136585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（彼女達は今や全国区のアイドルだぞ。星見市の）\n（ライブハウスに来る意味は薄い。なんだか怖いな……）",
      "startTime": 15.2021649544,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6633.33333340325,
          "startTime": 21.83549828780325
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 20.9021649545
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 20.9021649545
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう\nいえ、もうこんにちはかしら？",
      "startTime": 23.635498287803248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、神崎さん……ライブ前にどうしたんですか？\n三枝さんなら事務所にいると思いますが",
      "startTime": 30.968831621136584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 33.96883162113659
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、三枝さんは不在だったわ\nそうしたらかわりに貴方に会ったのよ",
      "startTime": 37.43549828780325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 40.702164954469914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "一つ、伝えておこうかと思って",
      "startTime": 40.702164954469914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "率直に言うわ\nうちの事務所――バンプロは貴方達を潰しに来てる",
      "startTime": 46.2021649544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 46.202164954469914
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 51.30216495446992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "私や葵の意向ではないわ\n私達はこんな姑息な手を使わなくても勝てるもの",
      "startTime": 54.16883162113659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 57.76883162113659
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、場所がどこであれ、そこにステージがあるなら\n断らないし、手も抜かないわ",
      "startTime": 61.86883162113659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 64.58932430629994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "自分達の意志じゃないって\n三枝さんに分かってほしくて、ここに？",
      "startTime": 66.455990973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんというより\n貴方の抱えるアイドル達にね",
      "startTime": 71.53065753663644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 74.06399086996977
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "私達がこそこそとズルいことをしているなんて\n思われるのは心外だもの",
      "startTime": 76.76399087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 78.88170057420993
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "私達はそんなつまらないことはしない",
      "startTime": 78.88170057420993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（なるほど）\n（プライドの高い彼女らしいな）",
      "startTime": 82.94274377311334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 85.30941043978
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "わざわざありがとうございます\n彼女達には俺から言っておきます",
      "startTime": 87.27607710644666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "貴方やっぱり素直なのね",
      "startTime": 89.88673858021417,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 92.15340524688085
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、星見プロが潰れる前にうちに転職したら？\nその方が貴方の将来のためだと思うわ",
      "startTime": 96.8867385802142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 99.9867385802142
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "ここもいつまで続くか分からないし",
      "startTime": 99.9867385802142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "すみませんが、それは出来ません",
      "startTime": 102.61379064892452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 105.31379064892448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん……",
      "startTime": 105.31379064892448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "……そう答えると思ったわ",
      "startTime": 107.11379064892452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 109.21379064892452
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、なんでそんなことを……",
      "startTime": 109.21379064892452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "試させてもらったのよ\n担当アイドルを捨てるような男だったらいらないわ",
      "startTime": 114.23517393444698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 118.00184060111364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "貴方は三枝さんとは違うようね",
      "startTime": 118.00184060111364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（まだデビュー前の神崎莉央と井川葵を見出したのが）\n（当時バンプロにいた三枝さんだ）",
      "startTime": 125.18247559244158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 127.75977731719304
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（だけど、彼女達LizNoirがデビューした直後）\n（三枝さんはバンプロを退職したんだっけ……）",
      "startTime": 131.7597773172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんにクビにされたら\n私に連絡しなさい",
      "startTime": 136.53449407592075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 138.53449407592075
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "うちの社長に話を通してあげる\n担当想いのいいマネージャーがいるって",
      "startTime": 141.4011607426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そうならないよう頑張ります",
      "startTime": 144.33449407592065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 146.53449412360436
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_01_03-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、そう\nでもトップを取るのは私たちLizNoirよ",
      "startTime": 148.86782745693765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 153.4344941236043
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
